---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Next Generation of Digital Marketing Firm in Myanmar" id="intro">
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logomark" class="h-32" />
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Established since <span class="text-primary">June 8, 2012</span> by young entrepreneurs from diverse and vibrant backgrounds, 
    evolx is a start-up company committed with <span class="text-primary">"the last full measure of devotion"</span> 
    to bring our clients the IT solutions and business ideas that will drastically bring 
    a <span class="text-primary">positive and impactful changes</span> in their business.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="https://docs.astro.build/"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-primary px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="telescope" class="h-8" />
      <span>Call To Discuss</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://astro.new/"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="rocket" class="h-8" />
      <span>Check Our Work</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
